  "The temperature in a greenhouse follows T(t) = 60 + 20sin(pi*t/12) degrees F over a 12-hour period [0, 12]. A botanist needs to know at what time the rate of temperature change equals the average rate. Find t.": "温室温度在12小时[0,12] 的T(t) = 60 + 20sin(pi*t/12) f 度之后。植物学家需要知道温度变化的速度在什么时候等于平均速度。查找 t。",
  "Average rate = [T(12)-T(0)]/12 = [60-60]/12 = 0. T'(t) = 20(pi/12)cos(pi*t/12). Setting T'(c) = 0 gives cos(pi*c/12) = 0, so pi*c/12 = pi/2, c = 6.": "平均速率 = [T(12)-T(0)]/12 = [60-60]/12 = 0。T'(t) = 20(pi/12)cos (pi*t/12)。设置 T'(c) = 0 give cs(pi*c/12) = 0, 所以pi*c/12 = pi/2, c = 6。",
  "A ball is thrown upward with position s(t) = -16t^2 + 64t feet. Over the interval [0, 2], at what time does the instantaneous velocity equal the average velocity?": "向上抛出一个球,其位置是 s(t) = -16t2 + 64 英尺。在间隔 [0, 2] 之间,瞬时速度何时等于平均速度?",
