  "A factory's production function is P(t) = 500 + 40t - t^2 units, where t is hours into the shift (0 <= t <= 8). The manager wants to know at what hour the production rate equals the average production rate over the shift.": "工厂的生产功能是P(t) = 500 + 40t - t2 单位, 其中t是轮班的时数 (0  t   (8)) 。 经理想知道,在哪个小时,生产率等于轮班的平均生产率。",
  "Average rate = [P(8)-P(0)]/8 = [(500+320-64)-500]/8 = 256/8 = 32. P'(t) = 40-2t. Setting 40-2c = 32 gives c = 4.": "平均比率 = [P(8)-P(0)]/8 = [(500+320-64-500)]/8 = 256/8 = 32. P'(t) = 40-2t. 设置 40-2c = 32 给予 c = 4。",
  "A swimmer's distance along a pool lane is s(t) = 3t^2 - 0.2t^3 meters for 0 <= t <= 10 seconds. The coach applies the MVT on [2, 8] to find when the swimmer's instantaneous speed equals the average speed. What approximate time does the coach find?": "游泳员在游泳池车道上的距离是 S(t) = 3t2 - 0.2t3米, 10秒。 教练在 [ 2, 8] 上应用MVT, 以寻找游泳员的瞬时速度等于平均速度。 教练找到的大约时间是多少 ?",
